comments: Giles III (SAC) makes incidental contact to Brooks' (MEM) arm after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Morant (MEM) turns his body into Fox (SAC) and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Bjelica (SAC) swipes down and makes incidental hand on ball contact during Jackson's (MEM) shot attempt.
Melton (MEM) leans forward as Bazemore (SAC) brings his arm backwards and makes inadvertent contact to his head.  Bazemore does not go through his space and dislodge him from his defensive position.
Bazemore (SAC) loses his balance on his own and not as a result of the marginal contact by Melton (MEM) during the drive to the basket.
Giles III (SAC) establishes legal position in Morant's (MEM) path during the pick and gives him a step to avoid contact.
Morant (MEM) makes incidental contact with Fox's (SAC) arm after the release of the ball and does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Giles III (SAC) briefly grasps Valanciunas (MEM) during the screen and disengages in the post.
Giles III (SAC) and Valanciunas (MEM) engage and disengage in the post.
Giles III (SAC) jumps vertically and maintains a legal vertical position contesting the play at the basket by Morant (MEM).
Giles III (SAC) slightly extends his arms as he disengages from contact with Valanciunas (MEM) in the lane.
Jackson (MEM) makes marginal contact with Bazemore's (SAC) arm before he picks up his dribble.
Fox (SAC) attempts to split Jackson (MEM) and Brooks (MEM) on the perimeter and Jackson makes inadvertent contact to the ball with his knee.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with Jackson's (MEM) arm as he gathers the loose ball.
Bogdanovic (SAC) maintains legal position contesting Melton's (MEM) driving shot attempt and absorbs the contact.
Brooks (MEM) commits a take foul on Bogdanovic (SAC).
Jackson (MEM) makes marginal contact with Barnes's (SAC) arm before the ball is cleanly deflected away.
Barnes (SAC) makes marginal contact with Jackson (MEM) as he gathers the loose ball and makes the pass.
Fox (SAC) makes hand on ball contact at the start of Morant's (MEM) drive and any ensuing contact is deemed incidental.
Bazemore (SAC) makes contact with Morant's (MEM) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Jackson (MEM) makes hand on ball contact and deflects the ball as Bjelica (SAC) gathers the inbound pass.
Brooks (MEM) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Fox (SAC) legally contests Jones's (MEM) jump shot attempt.
